packageJSON.name: fifa-autobuyer
packageJSON.description: Electron application boilerplate based on React, React Router, Webpack, React Hot Loader for rapid application development

scripts.test: cross-env NODE_ENV=test BABEL_DISABLE_CACHE=1 babel-node ./node_modules/istanbul/lib/cli cover ./node_modules/mocha/bin/_mocha -- --compilers js:babel-register --recursive --require ./test/setup.js test/**/*.spec.js test/**/**/*.spec.js
scripts.build: npm run build-main && npm run build-renderer
scripts.start-hot: cross-env HOT=1 NODE_ENV=development electron -r babel-register -r babel-polyfill ./main.development
scripts.package: cross-env NODE_ENV=production node -r babel-register -r babel-polyfill package.js

releases.name: FIFA Autobuyer v0.4.3
releases.body:
### If you have a previous version installed on Windows or OSX, this update will be installed automatically.  No need to download a new version.

# Release Notes
- Optimize sniping (#134) and bidding (reduce # of 461 errors)
- Potential fix for issues listing players bought via BIN (#137)

releases.name: FIFA 17 Autobuyer v0.4.0
releases.body:
### If you have a previous version installed on Windows or OSX, this update will be installed automatically.  No need to download a new version.

# Release Notes
- Added "Watch" tab to player details
  - Will watch active trades on selected player for 20 minutes and report details
  - Useful to determine whether or not a selected player is a good candidate for use in the AB
- Automatically bid max if it is only 2 steps up.
  - Example: current bid = 900, your max = 1000
    - Previously: AB would bid 950, causing you to potentially lose bid.
    - Now: AB will bid your max of 1000 to try and win the bidding war.

### If you have a previous version installed on Windows or OSX, this update will be installed automatically.  No need to download a new version.

releases.name: FIFA 17 Autobuyer v0.1.1
releases.body:
### If you have a previous version installed on Windows or OSX, this update will be installed automatically.  No need to download a new version.

# Release Notes
- Created a Tour of the app for new users
  - If you have no players in your list, the tour will start automatically
  - If you want to go through the tour, but have already used the app, you can click the red blinking beacon next to the search bar.
- Fixed bidding logic to not update watchlist if BIN Snipe Only mode is enabled
- Fixed a couple display bugs in the bidding log
